tica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:18px;color:#10243e;">Highest risk: large gaps without volume confirmation.</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" style="width:16px;padding:4px 7px 4px 0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:18px;color:#2563eb;">•</td><td style="padding:4px 0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:18px;color:#10243e;">Overall opening bias: cautiously positive.</td></tr></table><p style="margin:0 0 5px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:18px;color:#5f6f82;"><strong>Data timestamp:</strong> Jul 13, 2026, 6:55 a.m. EDT</p><p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:18px;color:#5f6f82;">Premarket prices may change rapidly before the opening bell.</p><p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:18px;color:#5f6f82;">Sources: <a href="https://example.com/market-data" style="color:#2563eb;text-decoration:underline;">Official market data</a></p><table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td style="padding:18px 0 24px;border-top:1px solid #dbe3ee;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:18px;color:#5f6f82;"><a href="https://marketbrief.example/preferences" style="color:#2563eb;text-decoration:underline;">Manage preferences</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;·&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://marketbrief.example/unsubscribe" style="color:#2563eb;text-decoration:underline;">Unsubscribe</a><br><span style="display:inline-block;margin-top:8px;">Market information only. Not investment advice.</span></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>",
  "text": "MARKETBRIEF
Premarket Brief
Monday, July 13, 2026

Hi Ritoban,

Top gaps, catalysts, risk levels, and what may move at the open.

1. PREMARKET SNAPSHOT — FACTS
S&P 500 futures: 5,640 (+0.2%)
Nasdaq futures: 20,360 (+0.3%)
Dow futures: 41,120 (+0.1%)
TSX indicator: 22,710 (+0.2%)
VIX: 14.8 (+0.4)
Oil: US$81.20 (+0.7%)
Gold: US$2,410 (-0.1%)
USD/CAD: 1.362 (+0.1%)

2. TOP PREMARKET MOVERS
NVDA | +2.4% | Above average | Sector demand update | High
SHOP | +1.3% | Moderate | Analyst commentary | Medium

3. MAJOR NEWS CATALYSTS
1. Technology futures firm
Semiconductors: Technology may lead early index movement.
2. Oil prices move higher
Canadian energy: Energy shares may receive support.

4. EARNINGS MOVERS
ABC | Revenue above estimates | +3.1% | Guidance remains the focus.

5. WATCHLIST IMPACT
TCS | +0.4% | Technology sector strength | Opening volume

6. OPENING STRATEGY NOTES
• Avoid chasing large opening gaps.
• Wait for volume confirmation.
• Watch support and resistance.
• Note elevated volatility.

7. MARKETBRIEF VIEW — INTERPRETATION
• Strongest setup: technology shows relative strength.
• Highest risk: large gaps without volume confirmation.
• Overall opening bias: cautiously positive.

PREMARKET DATA NOTE
Premarket prices may change rapidly before the opening bell.

Data timestamp: Jul 13, 2026, 6:55 a.m. EDT
Sources: Official market data (https://example.com/market-data)

Manage preferences: https://marketbrief.example/preferences
Unsubscribe: https://marketbrief.example/unsubscribe

Market information only. Not investment advice.",
}
`;

